{"tid":1012074,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈大師黃大仙求籤 股樓騰訊跌至年尾","createTime":"2019-02-07T09:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T13:57:54.000Z","uid":66271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"755de34f85f00177f765e4ea0149a597ed0ecf6c","tid":1012074,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190205/large/1549381847_4b84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190205%2Flarge%2F1549381847_4b84.jpg&h=1e3a4f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踏入豬年，沈大師初三向黃大仙求籤，結果如下︰<br />\n<br />\n港股︰68號籤<br />\n中吉，姜太公遇文王。宜放長線釣大魚，上半年較反覆，宜過了中秋，即10月﹑11月後，才有魚上釣。<br />\n<br />\n樓市︰95號籤<br />\n中籤，女蝸煉石補天。上半年樓價反覆，由年頭至中秋前或下跌10%至15%，想置業人士，可等年底入市。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊︰10號籤<br />\n中籤，蘇秦不第。騰訊（700）還有排跌，而且多阻滯，需要借東風，靠北水資金，去到年尾才好轉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b636514b505d7df75719b274feed83a33a5e1f00","tid":1012074,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:37:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c2b342052d14ea7bf2ccc70b8d255722a31d61f","tid":1012074,"uid":93649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"乜撚野技術分析都係假<br />\n信師傅得永生"},{"pid":"7155039cf52c8386e0e24c6f47deb31eebca3bd9","tid":1012074,"uid":162526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c2b342052d14ea7bf2ccc70b8d255722a31d61f","tid":1012074,"uid":93649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"乜撚野技術分析都係假<br />\n信師傅得永生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"2a67f44d4791dc851e6b495636e6f2682d155673","tid":1012074,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"掃貨"},{"pid":"77ad6cde9e121268f276561af0204f37e32